name: BLOOD
description: BLOOD is a 16mm snowboarding film capturing two brothers lives in the snow-capped mountains of North America, while hunting for the true value of snowboarding. Wyatt and Cory Stasinos who are bonded by blood, film themselves cheating death and living life on the edge in some of snowboarding's most remote and sought after locations. BLOOD will awaken your third eye.
